    "en": {
      "title": "Power outage at presidential inauguration?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Narendra Fernando told Tamilmirar that there was no power cut in Parliament during the inauguration ceremony of the President.",
        "It is to be noted that there are reports that electricity was suddenly cut off during the inauguration of the President and CIT investigations have been started in this regard."
      ],
